Subject: [PATCH 5/6] views: add web UI for webhook management

Add CRUD views for webhooks accessible to project maintainers.
The project detail page shows a link to manage webhooks when the
logged-in user is a maintainer.

Signed-off-by: Robin Jarry <robin@jarry.cc>
